VISUAL: "One pipeline, three stages." showing "MEG IN" flowing into "1 ENCODER" (signal -> keys) and "2 ALIGNER" (signal -> words).
AUDIO: 'magnetic scanner and not a simple cap of electrodes? Because signal quality is everything. The cheaper option, EEG, is so smeared by your skull that its error rate blows past 60%. MEG sees the brain far more'

[02:20] [scene:talk]
